metadata.name: Owls-Patron Birds #1
metadata.description:
**The owls**, patron birds of the goddess **Athena**, have historically been the symbols of **wisdom** and **knowledge** which inspired us to make the owl a central figure of our platform and create an NFT collection based on this unique character. Our cartooned collection of owl idols includes **Albert Einstein, Elvis Presley, Sherlock Holmes, Wolfgang Amadeus Mozart, Michael Jackson, Nicola Tesla, Frida Kahlo, Bruce Lee, Mohammed Ali, Salvador Dali, Virginia Woolf, and many more**. Here is one of them. We hope, you love them as much as we do.

**zero2hero NFTs** can be used as **[SocialFi](https://zero2hero.net/docs/SocialFi)** items. More and more social media giants are expanding the exploration of NFT integration into their platform(i.e. **Facebook/Meta**, **Instagram**, **Twitter**, **Reddit**, **YouTube**, **[zero2hero.net](https://zero2hero.net)**, and more). NFTs can be used on [**zero2hero website**](https://zero2hero.net), **iOS**, and **Android** Apps, **Metaverse**, and on other NFT/Social media spaces.

The collection was created by [**zero2hero team**](https://www.zero2hero.ltd/#team).
